title: DDFP 498: Week 6 recap, Jets' struggles & Who will win the AFC West?
itunes:title: DDFP 498: Week 6 recap, Jets' struggles & Who will win the AFC West?
description:
Ike Taylor and Maurice Jones-Drew take over the show in Shek's absence to discuss if the Cowboys' rookies are 1 & 2 in the MVP race, who's going to win the AFC West and who's the second best team in the AFC after the Patriots. Plus, the fellas break down what's going wrong with the Jets and how they could best improve. Then, the guys break down the best wins and worst losses from Week 6, highlighting the Chargers' and Jaguars' wins and the Steelers' surprising loss.
